com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.oauth

Class BasicIBMOAuthCredentials

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.oauth.BasicIBMOAuthCredentials
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AWSCredentials, IBMOAuthCredentials

    public class BasicIBMOAuthCredentials
extends Object
implements IBMOAuthCredentials
    Basic implementation of the IBMOAuthCredentials interface that allows callers to pass in the IBM api key and service instance id in the constructor.
